★ ★ ★ ★ ★  WAGmob: Over 350,000 paying customers from 175+ countries. ★ ★ ★ ★ ★  

WAGmob brings you a simple 'n easy on-the-go learning and reference for Psychology. A reference guide that teaches you the basics in a nice and organized manner.  


Features includes tutorials, quizzes and more.

App is continuously updated based on your feedback. Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.



Includes following tutorials:

Psychology Introduction,
Research in Psychology,
Biological Foundation of Behaviour,
State of Consciousness,
Sensation,
Perception,
Learning and Conditioning,
Memory,
Motivation,
Emotions,
Human Development,
Personality,
Cognition and Language,
Stress and Coping,
Psychological Disorders,
Treatment of Psychological Disorders,
Social Cognition and Influence.


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on Perception, Learning and Conditioning,
Quiz on Memory,
Quiz on Psychological Disorders.


Disclaimer for WAGmob Medical apps: 

1) The information in this app is for education purposes only.

2) Please do not take any action based on content of this app.

3) Always consult with your qualified health care provider before embarking on a new treatment, diet or fitness program. 

4) Please read detailed legal disclaimer before continuing with this app.



What is unique about WAGmob apps? 

1) A touch friendly, quick reference app, which is always in your pocket and always works (no data connection required).

2) A companion app for on-the-go, bite-sized learning.

3) Offers value for money (A lifetime of free updates).

4) Over 350,000 paying customers from 175+ countries.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and truly complete.

Our Mission: A WAGmob app in every pocket.

Please write to us Team@wagmob.com. We would love to improve this app.
